{"tid":1468953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：情報單位告知 中國派軍到香港邊境   白宫密切監視","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:09:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b00a149b42896997e3da32014d68abd92cd87395","tid":1468953,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:32:58.000Z","msg":"川普：情報單位告知 中國派軍到香港邊境<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-14<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普13日推文指出，美方情報單位告知，中國大陸政府往香港邊境部署軍隊，大家都該注意安全。<br />\n<br />\n川普另一則推文則寫道，他不理解為何香港發生的問題，許多人要責怪他與美國。<br />\n<br />\n川普稍早在新澤西州時回答媒體提問表示，香港局勢非常艱難，但他相信一切都能解決。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透報導，川普也說，希望香港在沒人傷亡的情況下解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n香港「反送中」示威持續，12日因大規模示威活動致香港機場停擺，13日再有示威者到機場集會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">彭博資訊上月底引述美國高級官員說法指出，中國軍力在香港邊界集結，白宫密切監視</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump<br />\n✔<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n Our Intelligence has informed us that the Chinese Government is moving troops to the Border with Hong Kong. Everyone should be calm and safe!<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"8d5a0de45714b219beebb1d94e1465e4223464be","tid":1468953,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:33:28.000Z","msg":"721     811"},{"pid":"0aba13b8356001a97a319a33c21a8dec1904de95","tid":1468953,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:37:55.000Z","msg":"721     811"},{"pid":"573d71ad601e55306dd40c4d2eb7b34aafeaf87a","tid":1468953,"uid":269118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:40:06.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"0f76216f1aae99bab86e99c601828293a81de4a8","tid":1468953,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:47:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"256e9c7e5beaa0f104478e26992ef1d6e7b74e0c","tid":1468953,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:51:39.000Z","msg":"幾時取消香港關係法"},{"pid":"423976c1bc15111fe5d52214e8ddd31d3f3af110","tid":1468953,"uid":160